---
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section id="about" class="py-32 container">
  <SectionHeader index="01" title="About" />
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
      <p>I'm a fullstack engineer who treats backend code like it's going into production on a Friday afternoon — because it usually is. My happy place is <span class="text-foreground">designing event-driven microservices</span>, taming gnarly business logic and making databases sing.</p>
      <p>Over the last few years I've shipped ERPs running across 9 sister concerns, built a food-delivery platform stitched together with Kafka and gRPC, and kept a South-African logistics engine humming through 3,000+ daily tracking events.</p>
      <p>I care about <span class="text-primary-container">Hexagonal Architecture</span>, <span class="text-secondary">DDD</span>, and the boring discipline of writing code that future-you (and your teammates) will actually enjoy reading.</p>
    </div>
    <aside class="md:col-span-5 surface-card p-8 self-start">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-4">// quick facts</p>
      <dl class="space-y-4 text-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-foreground">Based in</dt><dd class="font-medium">Dhaka, Bangladesh</dd></div>
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-foreground">Role</dt><dd class="font-medium">Backend Developer @ Defined Solution</dd></div>
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-foreground">Education</dt><dd class="font-medium">CSE, Dhaka International University</dd></div>
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-foreground">Currently into</dt><dd class="font-medium">Nest.js, RabbitMQ, Micro-Service, Distributed Systems</dd></div>
      </dl>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
